title: Index of Factory Payrolls, Boots and Shoes for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1919-1941 (2)--Original Data, 1939-1942. Data Are Adjusted To The 1939 Census Level. Source: Bureau Of Labor Statistics, "Employment And Payrolls".
